On this screen you can register, change and delete supplies. 
 

Should select a vehicle in the dropdown. Choose a station from the dropdown below. Choose between Petrol or Ethanol if vehicle is selected FLEX POWER, for other vehicles the fuel will be automatically selected. 
 

In the choice between Request Amount Paid or Requested Liters, type in the relevant field of your choice that other value will be generated automatically. 
 

Finally, enter the current mileage of your vehicle.
